<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不公平！”凯蒂喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我忙着卖蚯蚓的话，我不能做蚯蚓小组的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她踢了一下冰盆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，搭档。”卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你现在在做诱饵生意。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但今天是寻宝的完美星期六。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天是钓鱼的完美星期六，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也是卖鱼饵的完美星期六。”卢克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂看了一下大街对面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！“她说，“寻宝者们在拼克药店！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组又来了！哦，卢克！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她大喊道：“每个人都走在我们前面！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组一直很忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一张名片。”乔伊读着清单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来自托德先生的理发店。”卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把它放进了购物袋里了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一支印有公司名的笔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从柳树溪银行拿到的。”劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一张庭院打折公告。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这儿！”卡洛斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等一下。让我看看。”劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看那张纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个是今天，而且就在现在！”劳拉喜欢庭院打折。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们应该去寻宝，不是购物。”卡洛斯皱着眉头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这话没错。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以在打折的地方寻宝！”劳拉恳求道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这话也没错。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求你们了，求你们了！”劳拉恳求道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯看着曼尼叹了口气。“我放弃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太棒了！”劳拉叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组上了自行车向大街上骑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，凯蒂！嗨，卢克！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们经过脆皮派天堂时，他们喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要去哪里？”凯蒂喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但龙卷风小组已经过了桥，上了公路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“沿着箭头走！”劳拉边喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>边指着一个大大的粉色标志。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组经过黑莓路，然后经过了公墓路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉看到了另一个标志。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这儿转弯！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组骑上一座陡峭的小山，然后从另一边骑下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”曼尼尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在那儿！”劳拉喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在史蒂文森房子里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙卷风小组的自行车停在了一个旧农舍的车道上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好，史蒂文森阿姨！”他们大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史蒂文森阿姨在院子里，正在往桌子上摆放盘子和玻璃罐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们好，孩子们！”她回答说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来看看我们有什么。很多宝物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看看这些东西！”劳拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抓起一顶有黑色羽毛的红帽子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要五十美分！我看起来怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把一顶大草帽戴在乔伊的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“完美！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊把手伸进口袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一美元。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>草坪的桌子上放满了衣服、毯子、一盒盒的丝带、花边和纽扣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有旧工具、铜罐和空瓶子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有打字机、雨伞、马鞍和雪橇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“棒球卡！”曼尼说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯举起一个旧的柳树溪竞选徽章。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“选霍顿当市长。”他读道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不需要这些吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“需要！”劳拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就知道我们会在这里找到什么的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看看这些柳树溪的老照片。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉把手伸进盒子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一辆马车在大街上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿。”卡洛斯说，“这一定是老消防站。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看看这个。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉站在乔伊身后看着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一块墓碑。”劳拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“霍华德• 杰克逊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看上面的日期。”乔伊说，“1848年！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡洛斯说：“那比我们镇还老。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那可能是柳树溪最古老的坟墓！”乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要在公墓找它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想去公墓！”曼尼大声说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看起来很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，乔伊感到一只手搭在她的肩上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是史蒂文森阿姨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个坟墓不在公墓里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它比那个公墓还要古老。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它在哪儿？阿姨。”乔伊问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就在这儿的农场里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克逊夫妇是第一个在这里定居的家庭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个坟墓在他们家墓地里，穿过牧场就是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>88</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们想看看吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>89</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我们想！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>90</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊、卡洛斯和劳拉一起说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>